<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="shorten-v">shorten <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'ʃɔːtn/    美 /'ʃɔːrtn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-vt-vi">1.★ <strong>vt &amp; vi (使) 变短；缩短：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a shortened version of classics
经典著作的缩略版</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Smoking shortens your life.
吸烟会减寿。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Days shorten in winter.
冬季白天变短。</p></div></div>